enum FdoGeometryType

FdoGeometryType is an enumeration to denote the type of a Geometry.

Remarks:
This enumeration applies to types that derive from FdoIGeometry.
Enumerator:
FdoGeometryType_None  Indicates no specific type; used for "unknown", "don't care" or an incompletely constructed Geometry object.
FdoGeometryType_Point  Point type (FdoIPoint).
FdoGeometryType_LineString  LineString type (FdoILineString).
FdoGeometryType_Polygon  Polygon type (FdoIPolygon).
FdoGeometryType_MultiPoint  MultiPoint type (FdoIMultiPoint).
FdoGeometryType_MultiLineString  MultiLineString type (FdoIMultiLineString).
FdoGeometryType_MultiPolygon  MultiPolygon type (FdoIMultiPolygon).
FdoGeometryType_MultiGeometry  MultiGeometry type (FdoIMultiGeometry).
FdoGeometryType_CurveString  CurveString type (FdoICurveString).
FdoGeometryType_CurvePolygon  CurvePolygon type (FdoICurvePolygon).
FdoGeometryType_MultiCurveString  MultiCurveString type (FdoIMultiCurveString).
FdoGeometryType_MultiCurvePolygon  MultiCurvePolygon type (FdoIMultiCurvePolygon).
